forge script script/Deploy.s.sol --rpc-url base_sepolia

# Broadcast (actual deploy)
forge script script/Deploy.s.sol --rpc-url base_sepolia --broadcast

# With verification
forge script script/Deploy.s.sol --rpc-url base_sepolia --broadcast --verify
```

**Advanced features:**
- `vm.startBroadcast()` / `vm.stopBroadcast()` — only txs inside are sent
- Multi-chain deploys in one script
- CREATE2 deterministic addresses
- Resume failed broadcasts with `--resume`

